This header is a clean-room reverse-engineered implementation of the VST2
binary ABI. It does not use, reference, or contain any code from the
Steinberg VST2 SDK. It has been used by LMMS, Carla, Ardour, and other
open-source audio projects for over 20 years.

This copy is derived from the Carla project's vendored VeSTige header:
https://github.com/falkTX/Carla

The Keepsake project vendors this header under the same GPL v2+ terms.
